      "description": "Learn about mobile app development with React Native, a popular framework maintained by Facebook that enables cross-platform...",
      "content": "<h2>Overview</h2><p>This course picks up where&nbsp;<a>CS50</a>&nbsp;leaves off, transitioning from web development to mobile app development with React Native.<br /><br />The course introduces&nbsp;you to modern JavaScript (including ES6 and ES7) as well as to JSX, a JavaScript extension. Through hands-on projects,&nbsp;you&#39;ll gain experience with React and its paradigms, app architecture, and user interfaces. The course culminates in a final project for which&nbsp;you&#39;ll implement an app entirely of&nbsp;your own design.</p><h4>Taught by</h4><p>David J. Malan and Jordan Hayashi</p><h2>Help Center</h2><p>Most commonly asked questions about&nbsp;&nbsp;<a>EdX</a></p><ul><li><a>What is edX?</a></li><li><a>How do edX courses work?</a></li><li><a>How to sign up for edX courses?</a></li></ul><p><a>Browse&nbsp;More&nbsp;EdX Articles</a></p><h3>Highest Rated Courses</h3><ul><li><a>Machine Learning</a>&nbsp;via&nbsp;<a>Coursera</a><a>Stanford Universit</a><a>University of California, San Diego</a></li><li><a>Courser</a><a>Harvard University</a></li><li><a>CS50&#39;s Introduction to Computer Science</a>&nbsp;via&nbsp;<a>ed</a><a>University of Michigan</a></li><li><a>Programming for Everybody (Python)</a>&nbsp;via&nbsp;<a>Courser</a><a>University of Alberta</a></li><li><a>Dino 101: Dinosaur Paleobiology</a>&nbsp;via&nbsp;<a>Coursera</a></li></ul><p><a>Browse&nbsp;More&nbsp;Mobile Development courses</a></p><h2>Reviewfor edX&#39;s CS50&#39;s Mobile App Development with React Native</h2><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Based on&nbsp;<strong>1</strong>&nbsp;reviews</p><ul><li>5 star0%</li><li>4 star100%</li><li>3 star0%</li><li>2 star0%</li><li>1 star0%</li></ul><p><img src='https://ccweb.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.classcentral.com%2Fbundles%2Fclasscentralsite%2Fimages%2Freviews-illustration.png?auto=compress&amp;ixlib=php-2.1.1&amp;s=09c676a2263c9471dcd63ec990b0206' style='width:250px' /></p>",
